title: General Physics III
description: Charge and matter, electric field, electric potential, dielectrics, capacitance, current and resistance, electromotive force and circuits, magnetic fields, magnetic field of a moving charge, induced emf. 3 lectures, 1 laboratory. Fulfills GE B3 & B4.
prerequisites: PHYS 131 or HNRS 131 or PHYS 141, and MATH 142
